  "title": "A Brutal Welcome in the New Republic Brig",
  "summary": "Held in a New Republic military brig, the ex-Imperial Dareus receives a visit from Senator Del Marx, who trades wry banter with him about his arrest, the Sith lord Malign, and the impossibility of staying a bit player in the underworld. Their conversation is interrupted by the arrival of Admiral Doril Farnsworth, who flirts with Del, dismisses her, and has Dareus moved to a soundproofed interrogation room. There, Doril demands Dareus confess to ties with the Maffi syndicate and carry a warning back to them, alternately offering bribes and threats and revealing intelligence that Axel Vichten plans to bomb the Maffi compound. When Dareus refuses to cooperate and taunts him, Doril savagely beats him, breaking his nose and fabricating camera evidence of a murder confession before having guards continue the beating, leaving Dareus bloodied on the floor and plotting revenge.",
